**Problem:** IL2026/IL3050 at line 52 - `JsonSerializer.Deserialize<Dictionary<string, Dictionary<string, JsonElement>>>(span)`.

**Fix:** Replace the `JsonSerializer.Deserialize` call with `JsonDocument.Parse`. The code reads profile data and extracts resource types with their API versions. Replace the call like this:

```csharp
using (JsonDocument allProfileDoc = JsonDocument.Parse(BinaryData.FromStream(stream)))
{
    var armProfile = allProfileDoc.RootElement.GetProperty("resource-manager");
    foreach (var namespaceProp in armProfile.EnumerateObject())
    {
        var namespaceName = namespaceProp.Name;
        foreach (var apiVersionProperty in namespaceProp.Value.EnumerateObject())
        {
            var apiVersion = apiVersionProperty.Name;
            foreach (var resourceTypeItem in apiVersionProperty.Value.EnumerateArray())
            {
                string resourceTypeName = default;
                foreach (var property in resourceTypeItem.EnumerateObject())
                {
                    if (property.NameEquals("resourceType"))
                    {
                        resourceTypeName = property.Value.GetString();
                        break;
                    }
                }
                var resourceType = $"{namespaceName}/{resourceTypeName}";
                ResourceApiVersionOverrides[resourceType] = apiVersion;
            }
        }
    }
}
```

